text: The name Ana was given to six tropical cyclones in the Atlantic Ocean. So far, no tropical cyclone named Ana reached hurricane strength. *Tropical Storm Ana (1979) (see 1979 Atlantic hurricane season) *Tropical Storm Ana (1985) (see 1985 Atlantic hurricane season) *Tropical Storm Ana (1991) (see 1991 Atlantic hurricane season) *Tropical Storm Ana (1997) (see 1997 Atlantic hurricane season) *Tropical Storm Ana (2003) *Tropical Storm Ana (2009) *Tropical Storm Ana (2015)
title: Tropical Storm Ana
